\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid274882 CB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8916146\charrsid10629010 Take her a glass of milk.. And at other times she'd say ... they'd go out and they'd say, 'now you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
